Web development: PHP is used to create websites, applications, and other web-based content 
Content management systems: PHP is used to build content management systems (CMS) like WordPress, Joomla, and Drupal 
E-commerce platforms: PHP is used to develop e-commerce websites 
Web applications: PHP is used to create feature-rich web applications like social media platforms, forums, and customer relationship management (CRM) systems 
API development: PHP can be used to create APIs for web and mobile applications 
